## Security Considerations

### 11. RLS Policies
Always implement Row Level Security:
- Public read access for active items only
- Admin full access for management
- Proper authentication checks

### 12. Input Validation
Validate all inputs both client-side and server-side:
- Required fields
- Data types
- Length limits
- Sanitization

This pattern ensures consistency across your application and provides a solid foundation for managing any new tables you add to your Supabase database.
